{"tid":2041217,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞幸咖啡墮落的真相","createTime":"2020-05-29T05:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T08:48:12.000Z","uid":340796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"33c5e3f58a8111df23241ead8eb900ca18acc1b4","tid":2041217,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:50:10.000Z","msg":"根據華爾街日報翻查最新的紀錄，瑞幸咖啡被揭穿誇大銷售額：<br />\n<br />\n1. 向與陸正耀(瑞幸主席及最大投資者)有關聯的公司賣出超過1000萬張咖啡換領劵，而當中大多數的公司在<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中國知名度低</strong></span> (little-known companies in cities across China)。這類公司更曾在<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>深夜時份大手向瑞幸買入換領卷</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。(Rafts of orders sometimes came in during overnight hours.)<br />\n<br />\n2. 員工<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>利用個人賬戶購買咖啡劵</strong></span>，誇大2 - 3億人民幣的營業額<br />\n<br />\n3. 基於以上方式，大量資金流入瑞幸；瑞幸用作支付人力資源、原材料採購以及運輸。 但內部文件顯示，這類公司<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>當時並未存在</strong></span>。(Many didn&rsquo;t exist until April and May of 2019)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. 第3點提到的牽涉款項大概為10億人民幣。內部文件顯示，款項由一名梁姓女士處理。但瑞幸知情人士指<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無此人</strong></span>(fictitious)。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 付款的過程未有經過財務部的審核 (bypassed the chief financial officer who then didn&rsquo;t oversee Luckin&rsquo;s finance and treasury department)，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只獲COO錢治亞的批准</strong></span>(approved the payments and actively saw to the progress of the payment processes)。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 知情人士估計瑞幸利用虛假的資金鏈不斷循環誇大銷售及支出；<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但值得一提的是，仍未清楚第一筆的資金從何而來</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (It remains unclear what was the original source of funds to kick-start the transactions.)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/behind-the-fall-of-chinas-luckin-coffee-a-network-of-fake-buyers-and-a-fictitious-employee-11590682336?mod=hp_lead_pos5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fbehind-the-fall-of-chinas-luckin-coffee-a-network-of-fake-buyers-and-a-fictitious-employee-11590682336%3Fmod%3Dhp_lead_pos5&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33P56hpy2SSQtx6ElJ%2BvIbMI%3D&h=ac0567b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/behind-the-fall-of-chinas-luckin-coffee-a-network-of-fake-buyers-and-a-fictitious-employee-11590682336?mod=hp_lead_pos5</a>"},{"pid":"7ef7c68623de913cb5e893698778acbc6e6a48bf","tid":2041217,"uid":142965,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:54:45.000Z","msg":"左手交右手扮營業額 支那做假數標準招式"},{"pid":"c35a5e79ecf9eb5a8f0830c6d2a9d20fff831c06","tid":2041217,"uid":340796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ef7c68623de913cb5e893698778acbc6e6a48bf","tid":2041217,"uid":142965,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:54:45.000Z","msg":"左手交右手扮營業額 支那做假數標準招式"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:56:53.000Z","msg":"無限左交右, 右交左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc50c472c727e89384fabf69bbf61a0770ab9c8","tid":2041217,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"之前一日升番50%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過之前跌左97%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903e660f9d3ee86d029af613a3b8fb50aa7d7384","tid":2041217,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dc50c472c727e89384fabf69bbf61a0770ab9c8","tid":2041217,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"之前一日升番50%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"